# License Overview

This repository follows the [REUSE specification](https://reuse.software/).
Each source file declares its licensing via SPDX headers, and these headers are
the authoritative source of license information.

## Licensing Strategy

- **Firmware (`firmware/`)** is licensed under the **GNU General Public License v3.0 or later**.
- **Documentation and example hardware modifications (`docs/`)** are **dual-licensed**:
  - [Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/)
  - GNU General Public License v3.0 or later
  You may choose either license.
- **Vendored USB host component (`firmware/components/usb_host_hid`)** is licensed under the **Apache License 2.0**.

Full license texts can be found in the `LICENSES/` directory.
